{"tid":2418422,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"招人玩 GTA新FiveM RP Ser 尖沙咀碼頭","createTime":"2021-02-22T15:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T13:24:18.000Z","uid":138509,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b189053dcbbeb53f9c58cad862800aa1ad86b2e7","tid":2418422,"uid":138509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:05:49.000Z","msg":"咩係 GTA RP？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRP 顧名思義即係 Role-playing，代表玩家要係城市內實現自己角色。<br />\n如果你玩厭咗只有成為汪洋大盜嘅故事情節，咁加入RP ser就最適合你啦！<br />\n<br />\n係呢度，你可以成為警察、救護、整車佬、的士陳又或者黑社會... <br />\n甚至記者、漁夫或者巴士佬都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正職以外仲可以打劫或者撈毒<br />\n如果你唔想撈偏嘅，可以買返間便利店投資做生意<br />\n<br />\n咁做咩要入你個Ser？<br />\n我哋個ser特別在於有個賽馬會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會搞車隊比賽同埋其他唔同嘅活動～<br />\n另外Admin團隊亦成日推出唔同款式嘅車比各位愛車之人買入！<br />\n除咗賽車之外，亦都有拳賽、團隊槍戰甚至捉伊因等等！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，Server好歡迎新手～<br />\n除咗有新手金之外，更加有專人帶你融入！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即刻申請加入白名單：<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/es5VqXbSGv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Fes5VqXbSGv&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=3db94b66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/es5VqXbSGv</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CNDyvK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CNDyvK.jpg&h=bcfec93c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OU68VJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOU68VJ4.jpg&h=c1ba6811&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3euFaK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3euFaK.jpg&h=411a3e01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypin0aL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fypin0aL.jpg&h=41f3af83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0pqXXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0pqXXq.jpg&h=bcd16646&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e6cae9501d102e4ef0329ede2e567d13cda8305","tid":2418422,"uid":138509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"黎緊我地禮拜三 (24/2) 仲有三項鐵人大賽<br />\n有興趣玩既朋友記得早點入黎<br />\n夜晚930 到時見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qobTxx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qobTxx.jpg&h=7c1c5a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEjiyxx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEjiyxx.jpg&h=1faa2d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GH8Wkcx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGH8Wkcx.jpg&h=e6b8ebb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f872527e413d5cab1d1e912181ebe8367c44764d","tid":2418422,"uid":19126,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"電腦版真係多野玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337847624cb42926e1451df942321dc212bf1dda","tid":2418422,"uid":138509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f872527e413d5cab1d1e912181ebe8367c44764d","tid":2418422,"uid":19126,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"電腦版真係多野玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:14:39.000Z","msg":"快啲裝返個電腦版，借個張down gta再裝FiveM就玩到，唔洗買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c0066d49d0c67178ccefc0a1a6059185782d2e","tid":2418422,"uid":138509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:15:2